<script type="text/javascript">
                // <![CDATA[
                Appx.staticResourcesFolder = "/resource/1698880146000/assetsappx";
                //labels referenced within js that do not have their own VF component to hose them
                Appx.label = {
                    close: 'Close',
                    like : 'Like',
                    likes : 'likes',
                    reviewSubmit : 'Your review was submitted.',
                    reviewEdit : 'Your changes were saved.',
                    reviewDelete : 'This review has been deleted.',
                    reportAbuse : 'Your feedback was submitted. We\'ll investigate and take the appropriate action.'
                };

                domready(function () {
                    AppxSvgIE.init();
                });

                // We have an external SVG sprite. IE10 and IE11 don't like that.
                var AppxSvgIE = {

                    applySvgForIE : false,

                    init: function() {
                        var htmlEl = document.documentElement;
                        // both IE10 and IE11 would have class names "flexboxtweener" on the <html> tag at this point, thanks to modernizr. Edge or non-Microsoft browsers do not.
                        if (htmlEl.classList.contains('flexboxtweener')) {
                            AppxSvgIE.applySvgForIE = true;
                            AppxSvgIE.getSvgContent();
                        }
                    },
                    /*
                        Remoting call to get all the svg icons from the static resources
                     */
                    getSvgContent: function() {
                        Visualforce.remoting.Manager.invokeAction(
                                'AppxLayoutController.getSvgContent',
                                function (result, event) {
                                    if (event.status) {
                                        AppxSvgIE.SVG_CONTENT = result;
                                        var div = document.createElement("div");
                                        div.setAttribute('id', 'svg_sprite_IE');
                                        div.innerHTML = AppxSvgIE.SVG_CONTENT;
                                        document.body.insertBefore(div, document.body.childNodes[0]);
                                        AppxSvgIE.buildSVGForIE();
                                    } else {
                                        throw new Error("Something went wrong trying to get the svg content!");
                                    }
                                },
                                {buffer: false, escape: false}
                        );
                    },
                    /*
                        Gets the icon name/id, from the current svg icon, this one will be replaced
                    */
                    getIconName : function(useNode){
                        if (useNode){
                            var href = useNode.getAttribute('xlink:href');
                            if (href){
                                var parts = href.split('#');
                                if (parts.length > 1){
                                    return parts[1];
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    },
                    /*
                        Gets the symbol name from our dummy svg
                    */
                    getSymbolByName : function(iconName){
                        var dummySVGSprite = document.getElementById('svg_sprite_IE');
                        if (dummySVGSprite){
                            var symbols = dummySVGSprite.getElementsByTagName('symbol');
                            return symbols[iconName];
                        }
                    },
                    /*
                        This method does the magic of replace all the svg that are not rendered in the page and replaces them
                        with our svg icons from static resources (Internet Explorer treatment)
                    */
                    buildSVGForIE : function(){
                        var svgIcons = document.getElementsByTagName('svg');
                        for (var i = 0; i < svgIcons.length; i++) {
                            var currentSvg = svgIcons[i];
                            var useNode = currentSvg.getElementsByTagName('use')[0];
                            var iconName = AppxSvgIE.getIconName(useNode);
                            if (currentSvg && useNode && iconName){
                                var symbol = AppxSvgIE.getSymbolByName(iconName);
                                if (symbol){
                                    AppxSvgIE.replaceSVG(currentSvg, iconName);
                                }
                            }
                        }

                    },
                    /*
                        Sames as above function but it must to be used after a rerender
                    */
                    buildSVGForIEAfterRerender : function () {
                        if (AppxSvgIE.applySvgForIE === true){
                          AppxSvgIE.buildSVGForIE();
                        }
                    },
                    /*
                        Replaces the svg with the new svg icon obtainer from our dummy svg container
                     */
                    replaceSVG : function (currentSvg, iconName){
                        var container = currentSvg.parentElement;
                        var prefix = "slds-";
                        var svgns = "http://www.w3.org/2000/svg";
                        var xlinkns = "http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink";
                        var iconClassName = currentSvg.className.baseVal;
                        var svgroot = document.createElementNS(svgns, "svg");
                        svgroot.setAttribute("aria-hidden", "true");
                        svgroot.setAttribute("class", iconClassName);
                        svgroot.setAttribute("name", iconName);
                        svgroot.setAttribute("xmlns", svgns);
                        svgroot.setAttribute("xmlns:xlink", xlinkns);
                        // Add an "href" attribute (using the "xlink" namespace)
                        var shape = document.createElementNS(svgns, "use");
                        var svgPath = '#' + iconName;
                        shape.setAttributeNS(xlinkns, "xlink:href", svgPath);
                        svgroot.appendChild(shape);
                        container.replaceChild(svgroot, currentSvg);
                    }
                }

                // ]]>
            </script>

<script type="text/javascript">
                var userAnalyticsToken = 'c0831b81-c6e9-4030-ab6b-6349dae185fc';
                function loadPixelIframe(){
                    var base_url = 'https://appexchange.salesforce.com';

                    var iframe_element = document.getElementById('TrackingPixels');
                    iframe_element.removeEventListener("load", listenerLogic);
                    iframe_element.addEventListener("load", listenerLogic);

                    var whitelistedAttributes = JSON.parse('[]');
                    ScrubbedPageReferrer.init(whitelistedAttributes, base_url);

                    isAuthenticated = false;
                }
                function listenerLogic() {
                    var pixels = JSON.parse('[]');
                    SubscribeTrackingEvents.init(pixels);
                    Eventbus.publish('Pageload[appxStore]');
                    Eventbus.publish('Pageload[*]');
                    Eventbus.publish('Analytics[UserAuthenticatedfalse]');

                }
                loadPixelIframe();
            </script>

<div class="slds-global-header__item slds-global-header__item_search appx-global-header__item appx-global-header__item--search"><span id="j_id0:AppxLayout:header:appxheaderComp:j_id42">
<script type="text/javascript">
    //<![CDATA[
      var recentItems = {};

      AppxHeaderSearch.inAppExchangeSuffix = 'in AppExchange';

      var retrievedSuggestions = new Array();
    // Listening for a custom event here.
    // When that event gets triggered, we will go fetch the data for the search tray.
      document.body.addEventListener('appxShowSearchTray', appxFetchSearchTrayData, false);
            /**
       * Inside AppxHeaderSearchTray.initTray, a custom event will get triggered, when it is time to build the search tray.
       * On this page, we are listening for that event, and call this function at that time.
       * The search field and value are being passed in.
       */
      function appxFetchSearchTrayData(e) {
        
        var searchField = e.detail.searchField;
        var searchFieldValue = e.detail.searchFieldValue;
        if(searchFieldValue == ""){
            document.getElementById('search-box-remove').setAttribute('class', 'slds-hide');
          }else{
            document.getElementById('search-box-remove').setAttribute('class', 'slds-show');
          }
        // The type of data in the tray depends on the value inside the seach box.
          var trayType = 'recent';
          if (searchFieldValue !== "") {
              trayType = 'suggestions';
          }
        
        // The title of the tray depends on the type of tray.
        // Putting the title here, allows us to translate it into a different language.
          var trayTitle = 'Recent Items';
          if (searchFieldValue !== "") {
              trayTitle = 'in AppExchange';
          } 
        
        // The urlPrefix depends on the type of tray.
          var urlPrefix = '/listingDetail?listingId=';
          if (searchFieldValue !== "") {
              urlPrefix = 'https://appexchange.salesforce.com/appxSearchKeywordResults?keywords=';
          }
           
          var appxBuildSearchTrayEvent = new CustomEvent('appxBuildSearchTray',{
                            detail: {
                                searchField: searchField,
                                searchFieldValue: searchFieldValue,
                                trayType: trayType,                               
                                trayTitle: trayTitle,
                                urlPrefix: urlPrefix
                            }
                        });

          if (searchFieldValue === "" && true){
             showRecentItems(appxBuildSearchTrayEvent);
          }

          if (searchFieldValue !== "" && true) {
             showSuggestions(appxBuildSearchTrayEvent,searchFieldValue);
          }        
      } 

      function showRecentItems(appxBuildSearchTrayEvent){          
          appxBuildSearchTrayEvent.detail.trayData = recentItems;
          document.body.dispatchEvent(appxBuildSearchTrayEvent);    
      }

      function showSuggestions(appxBuildSearchTrayEvent, keywords){        
          if(retrievedSuggestions !== undefined && retrievedSuggestions[keywords] !== undefined){                  
              appxBuildSearchTrayEvent.detail.trayData = retrievedSuggestions[keywords];
              document.body.dispatchEvent(appxBuildSearchTrayEvent);
          }else{             
             getSuggestions(appxBuildSearchTrayEvent,keywords);
          } 
      }

      function getRecentItems() {
          Visualforce.remoting.Manager.invokeAction(
              'AutocompleteSearchBoxController.getRecentViewedListings',Appx.getCookie("apex__appxSearch"), 'a0O30000000ou5QEAQ',
              function(result, event){
                  if (event.status) {      
                      var result = JSON.stringify(result).replace(/amp;/g,'').replace(/&#39;/g,"'");
                      recentItems = JSON.parse(result);                      
                  } else {
                      console.log(event.message);
                  }
              }, 
              {escape: true}
          );
      } 

      function getSuggestions(appxBuildSearchTrayEvent, keywords) {                  
          Visualforce.remoting.Manager.invokeAction(
              'AutocompleteSearchBoxController.getSuggestions', keywords, 'en',              
              function(result, event){
                  if (event.status) {
                      appxBuildSearchTrayEvent.detail.trayData = result;
                      retrievedSuggestions[keywords] = result;                        
                      document.body.dispatchEvent(appxBuildSearchTrayEvent);
                                   
                  } else {
                      console.log(event.message);
                  }
              }, 
              {escape: true}
          );
      }      

      /**
       * Most actions related to the search box are done from the search tray.
       * But sometimes we just want a 'simple search':
       * The user types a term and hits Enter/Return before there is a tray.
       * In that case, we can just call this function and go to the search page with the term the user typed.
       * This is being used inside AppxHeaderSearchTray.selectTrayItem()
       */
      function appxSimpleSearch(searchQuery) {
        document.location = 'https://appexchange.salesforce.com/appxSearchKeywordResults?keywords=' + encodeURIComponent(searchQuery) + '&searchType=simpleSearch';
      } 

      //getting the items so we can cache them and it will be faster for the user
      getRecentItems();
         
      function removeKeywords(){
        var searchField = document.getElementById('appx-search-01');
        searchField.value = '';
        var searchQuery = '';
        // Create a custom event that will be used in the search.component
        var appxShowSearchTrayEvent = new CustomEvent('appxShowSearchTray',{
            detail: {
                searchFieldValue: searchQuery,
                searchField: searchField
            }
        });
        // Trigger this custom event
        document.body.dispatchEvent(appxShowSearchTrayEvent);
      }
    //]]>
  </script>

            loginSsoUrl: "https://appexchange.salesforce.com/services/auth/sso/LoginPortal",

        var tbidHeader = new TrailblazerIdentityHeader(urls);
        tbidHeader.init();

        window.onInitTrailblazerIdentitySso = function(){
            tbidHeader.onInitWithTrailblazerIdentity();
        };

        window.onLoginTrailblazerIdentitySso = function(identity){
            tbidHeader.onLoginWithTrailblazerIdentity(identity);
        };

<script>
        /* <![CDATA[ */
        var AppxSaveListener = {

            theTile : null,
            btn        : null,
            listingName    : [],

            /*
            * @param e - the event recieved
            */
            appxSaveListing : function(e) {

            // the listing to save
                AppxSaveListener.theTile = (e.detail.tile)? e.detail.tile : null;
                AppxSaveListener.btn = e.detail.btn;
                AppxSaveListener.listingName.push((e.detail.listingName)? e.detail.listingName : AppxSaveListener.theTile.getAttribute('data-listing-name'));

            var state = e.detail.state;
            var savedlistingId = e.detail.listingId;
            //If user is not logged in, we will redirect to login
            if('false' == 'false') {
                window.location.href = 'https://appexchange.salesforce.com/services/auth/sso/LoginPortal?startURL=%2FuserSetup%3Fgt%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fappexchange.salesforce.com%252FappxStore%253Ftype%253DApp';
            } else {
                if(state === 'save') {
                    // This is where we make the call to save the listing to the Saved List
                    saveListingAction(savedlistingId);
                } else {
                    removeListingAction(savedlistingId);
                }                
            }
            },
        };

        // Listening for a custom event here.
        // When that event gets triggered, we will go add the listing to the Saved Listing
        document.body.addEventListener('appxTileSaveBtn', AppxSaveListener.appxSaveListing, false);
        document.body.addEventListener('appxListingDetailsFooterSaveBtn', AppxSaveListener.appxSaveListing, false);
        /* ]]> */
    </script><span id="j_id0:AppxLayout:header:appxheaderComp:loginPageRedirectAction">
<script type="text/javascript">
        /* <![CDATA[ */
            function loginPageRedirect(){
                window.location.href = 'https://appexchange.salesforce.com/services/auth/sso/LoginPortal?startURL=%2FuserSetup%3Fgt%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fappexchange.salesforce.com%252FappxStore%253Ftype%253DApp';
            }
            
        /* ]]> */
        </script></span><span id="j_id0:AppxLayout:header:appxheaderComp:saveCompletedActions">
<script type="text/javascript">
        /* <![CDATA[ */
            var AppxSaveManager = {
            //The server action completed, we need to update the Save button to its new state
                saveCompleted : function() {
                //Refresh heart icon quantity
                var appxUpdateFavoritesCountEvent = new CustomEvent('appxUpdateFavoritesCount');
                document.body.dispatchEvent(appxUpdateFavoritesCountEvent);

                    // switches to the new state
                    var currentState = "";
                    var newState = (currentState === 'save') ? 'saved' : 'save';

                // 1) create a custom event that will be used in the AppxTile plugin
                var appxTileWasSavedEvent = new CustomEvent('appxTileWasSaved',{
                    detail: {
                            theTile: AppxSaveListener.theTile,
                            btn: AppxSaveListener.btn,
                        state: newState
                    }
                });
                // 2) trigger this custom event
                document.body.dispatchEvent(appxTileWasSavedEvent);

                    // 1) create a custom event that will be used in the AppxListingDetailsFooter plugin
                    var appxListingFooterWasSavedEvent = new CustomEvent('appxListingDetailsFooterWasSaved',{
                        detail: {
                            btn: AppxSaveListener.btn,
                            state: newState
            }
                    });
                    // 2) trigger this custom event
                    document.body.dispatchEvent(appxListingFooterWasSavedEvent);

                    // 3 Shows toast message
                    if (AppxSaveListener.listingName)
                      for (var i = 0; i < AppxSaveListener.listingName.length; i++) {
                        AppxSaveManager.showToast(currentState, AppxSaveListener.listingName[i]);
                        AppxSaveListener.listingName.remove(AppxSaveListener.listingName[i]);
                      }
                      

                },

                /**
                 *
                 * @param state - state of the listing
                 * @param lstName - listing name
                 */
                showToast : function(state, lstName){

                    //Here we are receiving the new state of the listing, if it was saved, then we receive "Saved". If it was removed we will receive "Save"
                    if (state === 'save') {
                        ToastManager.createToast({
                            duration: ToastManager.duration.medium,
                            severity: ToastManager.severity.success,
                            title: '{0} has been added to your saved listings.'.replace('{0}', lstName)
                        });
                    } else {
                        ToastManager.createToast({
                            duration: ToastManager.duration.medium,
                            severity: ToastManager.severity.info,
                            title: '{0} has been removed from your saved listings.'.replace('{0}', lstName)
                        });
                    }
                },
            };
            /* ]]> */
        </script></span>

<script>
  /* <![CDATA[ */

  var spinnerData;
     var isResetFilters = false;
     var inSearchPage = false;

  // Translations are important.
  // The following strings are used inside the JS for filtering. We put these in the page so we can use the correct language.
  // These override the strings inside the JS.
  AppxFilter.showAllString = 'Select All';
  AppxFilter.onlyString = 'only';
  // Do we want buttons on the desktop? We can use buttons on the desktop enabling UseFilterButtonsOnDesktop feature flag.
  if(inSearchPage){
   AppxFilter.desktopButtons = true;
  }else{
   AppxFilter.desktopButtons = true;
  }

  // When the APPLY (or CLEAR) button gets clicked, the JS will call the following function
  // OR if we don't have buttons, changing a form element will do the same.
  AppxFilter.submit = function(isReset) {
   var dataValue, splitStr, key, val;
   var displayedMenu = document.getElementsByClassName('appx-displayed-filters')[0];
   var checkboxes = [];
   if(inSearchPage){
    if(displayedMenu){
     checkboxes = displayedMenu.querySelectorAll('input[class="appx-filter-checkbox"]:checked');
    }
   }else{
    checkboxes = document.querySelectorAll('input[class="appx-filter-checkbox"]:checked');
   }
   var keyMap = {};
   isResetFilters = isReset;

   for (var i = 0; i < checkboxes.length; i++) {
    dataValue = checkboxes[i].getAttribute("data-value");
    splitStr = dataValue.split('=');
    key = (splitStr.length > 1) ? splitStr[0] : null;
    val = (splitStr.length > 1) ? splitStr[1] : splitStr[0];

    if(key) {
     if(keyMap[key]) {
       
      // This is when multiple values are applied to the same filter, for example languages. example: lg=en#es#fi. 
      // Then, is parsed in the filterParams string as lg=en,lg=es,lg=fi
      keyMap[key] += '#' + val; 
     } else {
      keyMap[key] = val;
     }
    } else {
     if(keyMap['filter']) {
      keyMap['filter'] += ',' + val;
     } else {
      keyMap['filter'] = val;
     }
    }
   }

   //Country/state handler
   var countryObj = document.getElementById('select_country');
   if(countryObj != undefined){
    val = countryObj.value;
    if(val != ' '){
     if(keyMap['filter']) {
      keyMap['filter'] += ',' + val;
     } else {
      keyMap['filter'] = val;
     }
    }
   }
   var stateObjs = document.getElementsByClassName('appx-state-options');
   for(var i = 0 ; i < stateObjs.length ; i++){
    if(stateObjs[i].style.display == 'block'){
     val = stateObjs[i].value;
     if(val != ' '){
      if(keyMap['filter']) {
       keyMap['filter'] += ',' + val;
      } else {
       keyMap['filter'] = val;
      }
     }
    }
   }

   var filterParams = '';
   for (var property in keyMap) {
       if (keyMap.hasOwnProperty(property)) {
        if (property != 'filter'){
            if(filterParams) {
             if (keyMap[property].indexOf('#') !== -1) {
              var propertiesArray = keyMap[property].split('#');
              for (var i = 0; i < propertiesArray.length; i++) {
               filterParams += ',' + property + '=' + propertiesArray[i];              
        }
             } else {
              filterParams += ',' + property + '=' + keyMap[property]; 
             }            
            } else {
             if (keyMap[property].indexOf('#') !== -1) {
              var propertiesArray = keyMap[property].split('#');
              for (var i = 0; i < propertiesArray.length; i++) {
               filterParams += property + '=' + propertiesArray[i];
               if (propertiesArray.length != (i-1)) {
                filterParams += ','; 
               }              
        }
             } else {
              filterParams = property + '=' + keyMap[property];
             }            
            }
        } else {
         if (filterParams == ''){
          filterParams += keyMap['filter'];
         }
         else{
          filterParams += ',' + keyMap['filter'];
         }
        }
       }
   }
   // Show content spinner
   spinnerData = AppxSpinnerManager.wholePageOrContent('content');
   if(inSearchPage){
    var group = document.getElementsByClassName('appx-store-checkbox');
    var storesString = '';
    for (var i=0; i<group.length; i++) {
           if (group[i].checked) {
            if (storesString == ''){
          storesString += group[i].getAttribute('data-value');
         }
         else{
          storesString += ';'+group[i].getAttribute('data-value');
         }
           }
          }

          if(isReset == 'true'){
     resetFilters(filterParams, storesString, isReset);
    }else{
     applyFilters(filterParams, storesString, isReset);
    }
      }else{
       if(isReset == 'true'){
                    history.pushState({filtersStatus: 'Reset'}, null, null);
                } else {
                    history.pushState({filtersStatus: 'Applied',filterParams:filterParams}, null, null);
                }
    applyFilters(filterParams, isReset);
   }

   
  }

  function afterApplyFilters() {
   AppxSpinnerManager.hide(spinnerData.containerId);
   AppxTile.init();
   if(true){
    AppxFilter.init();
    AppxTooltip.init();
   }
   if (isResetFilters == 'true') {
    if(false){
     AppxFilter.init();
    }
    AppxBanner.init();
   }
  }

  function updateFilterTree() {
   var group = document.getElementsByClassName('appx-store-checkbox');
   var showKey = false;
   var isApp = false;
   var isCmp = false;
   var isBoltDataFlows = false;
   var isSvc = false;
   var isContent = false;

         for (var i=0; i<group.length; i++) {
          if (group[i].checked) {
              var currentScope = group[i].getAttribute('data-value');
              if(currentScope == 'Apps'){
               isApp = true;
              }else if(currentScope == 'Components'){
               isCmp = true;
              }else if(currentScope == 'Data' || currentScope == 'BoltTemplate' || currentScope == 'Flows'){
               isBoltDataFlows = true;
              }else if(currentScope == 'Services'){
               isSvc = true;
              }else if(currentScope == 'Contents'){
               isContent = true;
              }
             }
         }
         if((isApp && isCmp) || (isApp && isBoltDataFlows) || (isCmp && isBoltDataFlows) || ((isApp || isCmp || isBoltDataFlows) && (isSvc || isContent))){
          showKey = true;
          if(isBoltDataFlows && isContent && !isApp && !isCmp && !isSvc){
              toggleFilters();
             }else{
              toggleFilters('Key');
             }
            }else if(isApp && !showKey){
             toggleFilters('App');
            }else if(isCmp && !showKey){
             toggleFilters('Cmp');
            }else if(isSvc && !showKey){
             toggleFilters('Svc');
            }else{
             toggleFilters();
            }
  }

  function toggleFilters(toShow){
   var element = document.getElementsByClassName("appx-displayed-filters")[0];
   if(element){
    element.classList.remove("appx-displayed-filters");
    element.classList.add("appx-form-section__extra-hidden");
   }
   if(toShow){
    document.querySelector('[filter-type="'+toShow+'"]').classList.add("appx-displayed-filters");
    document.querySelector('[filter-type="'+toShow+'"]').classList.remove("appx-form-section__extra-hidden");
   }
  }

  function delayedUpdateFilterTree(){
   setTimeout(function(){updateFilterTree(); }, 100);
  }

  updateFilterTree();

  function addFilterLinksListener() {
   var filterLinks = Array.prototype.slice.call(document.getElementsByClassName('appx-form-element__label-link')).concat(Array.prototype.slice.call(document.getElementsByClassName('appx-form-element__legend-link-show')));

   for(var i = 0; i < filterLinks.length; i++) {
    if(!filterLinks[i].classList.contains('appx-listener-added')){
     filterLinks[i].addEventListener('click', function() {
      addFilterLinksListener();
      updateFilterTree();
     }, false);
    }
    filterLinks[i].classList.add("appx-listener-added");
   }
  }

  document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", addFilterLinksListener);

  domready(function(){
            if(window.performance.navigation.type == 2 && history.state != null && history.state.filtersStatus == 'Applied'){
                spinnerData = AppxSpinnerManager.wholePageOrContent('content');
                applyFilters(history.state.filterParams, false);
            } else{
                history.pushState({filtersStatus: 'NoAction'}, null, null);
            }
        });

  /* ]]> */
 </script>

</span><span class="appx-tile-feature-group" id="j_id0:AppxLayout:j_id2721:0:j_id2724:appxTile:j_id2771:j_id2772:j_id2942"><span class="appx-tile-feature appx-tile-feature-category" id="j_id0:AppxLayout:j_id2721:0:j_id2724:appxTile:j_id2771:j_id2772:j_id2943">

<script>
     // <![CDATA[

                    var AppxPostJob = {
                     skills : [],
                     categories : [],
                     eventButtonSubmit: null,
                        init: function() {
                            var btn = document.getElementById('appx_btn_postjob');
                            if (btn) {
                                btn.addEventListener('click', AppxPostJob.submit, false);
                            }
                            var deleteBtn = document.getElementById('appx_btn_deletejob');
                            if (deleteBtn) {
                                deleteBtn.addEventListener('click', AppxPostJob.delete, false);
                            }
                            AppxPostJob.markCheckboxes();
                            AppxPostJob.priceBlockInit();
                            AppxPostJob.dateBlockInit();
                            AppxPostJob.locationBlockInit();
                            AppxPostJob.closeEvents();
                        },
                        submit: function(e) {
                            if (AppxPostJob.validate() === false) {
                             AppxPostJob.eventButtonSubmit = e;
                             AppxPostJob.getCheckboxes();
                                // disabling buttons and showing spinner on button
                                Appx.showSpinnerButton('appx_btn_postjob');
                                Appx.disableButton('appx_btn_postjob');
                                Appx.disableButton('appx_btn_deletejob');
                                Appx.disableButton('appx_btn_canceljob');

                                title = document.getElementById('input_job_title').value;
                                description = document.getElementById('textareajob_descr').value;

                                isStartImmediately = false;
                                if (document.getElementById('radio_date_imm').checked) {
                                 isStartImmediately = true;
                                }

                                isFixedPrice = false;
                                if (document.getElementById('radio_price_fixed').checked) {
                                 isFixedPrice = true;
                                }

                                isAnyLocation = false;
                                country = '';
                                if (document.getElementById('radio_location_any').checked) {
                                 isAnyLocation = true;
                                } else{
                                    country = document.getElementsByClassName('appx-select-country')[0];
                                    AppxPostJob.country = country.value;
                                }
                                appxPostJob(title, description, AppxPostJob.skills.join(';'), AppxPostJob.categories.join(';'), isStartImmediately, isFixedPrice, isAnyLocation, country.value);
                            }
                        },
                        closeEvents: function() {
                         document.getElementById('appx_btn_canceljob').addEventListener('click', AppxPostJob.markCheckboxes, false);
                            document.getElementById('appx_btn_closejob').addEventListener('click', AppxPostJob.markCheckboxes, false);
                        },
                        finishSaveJob: function(e) {
                         Appx.hideModalCancel(AppxPostJob.eventButtonSubmit);
                            Appx.hideSpinnerButton('appx_btn_postjob');
                            Appx.enableButton('appx_btn_postjob');
                            Appx.enableButton('appx_btn_deletejob');
                            Appx.enableButton('appx_btn_canceljob');

                            if ("") {
                             ToastManager.createToast({duration: ToastManager.duration.medium, severity: ToastManager.severity.error, title: ""});
                            } else {
                             if (false) {
                              ToastManager.createToast({duration: ToastManager.duration.medium, severity: ToastManager.severity.success, title: "Your changes have been saved."});
                             } else {
                              ToastManager.createToast({duration: ToastManager.duration.medium, severity: ToastManager.severity.success, title: "Your job has been posted successfully"});
                             }
                            }
                            AppxPostJob.markCheckboxes();
                        },
                        delete: function(e) {
                            var confirmDelete = confirm("Are you sure that you want to delete the job?");
                            if (confirmDelete == true) {
                             AppxPostJob.eventButtonSubmit = e;
                             Appx.showSpinnerButton('appx_btn_deletejob');
                                Appx.disableButton('appx_btn_postjob');
                                Appx.disableButton('appx_btn_deletejob');
                                Appx.disableButton('appx_btn_canceljob');
                                appxDeleteJob();
                            }
                        },
                        finishDeleteJob: function() {
                         Appx.hideModalCancel(ListingDetails.eventButtonSubmit);
                            Appx.hideSpinnerButton('appx_btn_deletejob');
                            Appx.enableButton('appx_btn_postjob');
                            Appx.enableButton('appx_btn_deletejob');
                            Appx.enableButton('appx_btn_canceljob');

                            if ("") {
                             ToastManager.createToast({duration: ToastManager.duration.medium, severity: ToastManager.severity.error, title: ""});
                            } else {
                             ToastManager.createToast({duration: ToastManager.duration.medium, severity: ToastManager.severity.success, title: "This job has been deleted successfully"});
                            }
                        },
                        validate: function() {
                            var form = document.getElementsByClassName('appx_applyjob_form')[0];
                            var errors = AppxForm.validateForm(form);
                            return errors;
                        },
                        hideAllExtraBlocks: function(formBlockOuter) {
                            var extraBlocks = formBlockOuter.getElementsByClassName('appx-form-section__extra');
                            for (var i = 0; i < extraBlocks.length; i++) {
                                extraBlocks[i].classList.add('appx-form-section__extra-hidden');
                                AppxPostJob.tempDisableRequired(extraBlocks[i]);
                            }
                        },
                        tempDisableRequired: function(extraBlock) {
                            var reqEls = extraBlock.querySelectorAll('.appx-required');
                            for (var i = 0; i < reqEls.length; i++) {
                                reqEls[i].classList.add('appx-required-temp-disabled');
                            }
                        },
                        enableRequired: function(extraBlock) {
                            var reqEls = extraBlock.querySelectorAll('.appx-required');
                            for (var i = 0; i < reqEls.length; i++) {
                                reqEls[i].classList.remove('appx-required-temp-disabled');
                            }
                        },
                        priceBlockInit: function() {
                            var radioFixed = document.getElementById('radio_price_fixed');
                            var radioHourly = document.getElementById('radio_price_hourly');
                            radioFixed.addEventListener('click', AppxPostJob.priceBlock, false);
                            radioHourly.addEventListener('click', AppxPostJob.priceBlock, false);
                            AppxPostJob.priceBlock();
                        },
                        priceBlock: function(e) {
                            var radioFixed = document.getElementById('radio_price_fixed');
                            var radioHourly = document.getElementById('radio_price_hourly');
                            var formBlockOuter = document.getElementById('appx_form_block_price');
                            AppxPostJob.hideAllExtraBlocks(formBlockOuter);
                            if (radioFixed.checked) {
                                var fixedExtra = document.getElementById('appx_price_fixed__extra');
                                fixedExtra.classList.remove('appx-form-section__extra-hidden');
                                AppxPostJob.enableRequired(fixedExtra);
                            }
                            if (radioHourly.checked) {
                                var hourlyExtra = document.getElementById('appx_price_hourly__extra');
                                hourlyExtra.classList.remove('appx-form-section__extra-hidden');
                                AppxPostJob.enableRequired(hourlyExtra);
                            }
                        },
                        dateBlockInit: function() {
                            var radioImm = document.getElementById('radio_date_imm');
                            var radioDate = document.getElementById('radio_date_date');
                            radioImm.addEventListener('click', AppxPostJob.dateBlock, false);
                            radioDate.addEventListener('click', AppxPostJob.dateBlock, false);
                            AppxPostJob.dateBlock();
                        },
                        dateBlock: function(e) {
                            var radioImm = document.getElementById('radio_date_imm');
                            var radioDate = document.getElementById('radio_date_date');
                            var formBlockOuter = document.getElementById('appx_form_block_date');
                            AppxPostJob.hideAllExtraBlocks(formBlockOuter);
                            if (radioDate.checked) {
                                var dateExtra = document.getElementById('appx_date_date__extra');
                                dateExtra.classList.remove('appx-form-section__extra-hidden');
                                AppxPostJob.enableRequired(dateExtra);
                            }
                        },
                        locationBlockInit: function() {
                            var radioAny = document.getElementById('radio_location_any');
                            var radioSpecific = document.getElementById('radio_location_specific');
                            radioAny.addEventListener('click', AppxPostJob.locationBlock, false);
                            radioSpecific.addEventListener('click', AppxPostJob.locationBlock, false);
                            AppxPostJob.locationBlock();
                            var selectCountry = document.getElementsByClassName('appx-select-country')[0];
                            if (selectCountry) {
                             selectCountry.addEventListener('change', AppxPostJob.showHideState, false);
                         }
                            AppxPostJob.showHideState();
                        },
                        locationBlock: function(e) {
                            var radioAny = document.getElementById('radio_location_any');
                            var radioSpecific = document.getElementById('radio_location_specific');
                            var formBlockOuter = document.getElementById('appx_form_block_location');
                            AppxPostJob.hideAllExtraBlocks(formBlockOuter);
                            if (radioSpecific.checked) {
                                var specExtra = document.getElementById('appx_location_specific__extra');
                                specExtra.classList.remove('appx-form-section__extra-hidden');
                                AppxPostJob.enableRequired(specExtra);
                            }
                        },
                        showHideState: function() {
                            country = document.getElementsByClassName('appx-select-country')[0];
                            var stateBlock = document.getElementById('appx_location_state');
                            var state = document.getElementsByClassName('appx-select-state')[0];
                            AppxPostJob.country = country.value;
                            if (country) {
                             if (country.value === "US" || country.value === "CA" || country.value === "JP") {
                                 stateBlock.classList.remove('appx-form-element-hidden');
                                 state.classList.remove('appx-required-temp-disabled');
                             } else {
                                 stateBlock.classList.add('appx-form-element-hidden');
                                 state.classList.add('appx-required-temp-disabled');
                             }
                         }
                        },
                        getCheckboxes: function() {
       var skills = document.getElementsByClassName('appxSkills');
                            var categories = document.getElementsByClassName('appxCategories');
                            AppxPostJob.skills = [];
                            AppxPostJob.categories = [];
       for (var i=0; i<skills.length; i++)  {
        if (skills[i].checked) {
         AppxPostJob.skills.push(skills[i].dataset.value);
        }
       }
                            for (var i=0; i<categories.length; i++){
                             if (categories[i].checked) {
         AppxPostJob.categories.push(categories[i].dataset.value);
        }
                            }
                        },
                        markCheckboxes: function() {
       var checkboxes = document.querySelectorAll('.appxCategoriesChecked,.appxSkillsChecked');
       for (var i=0; i<checkboxes.length; i++)  {
          checkboxes[i].checked = true;
       }
       if (false) {
        document.getElementById('radio_price_fixed').checked = true;
       } else {
        document.getElementById('radio_price_hourly').checked = true;
       }
       if (false) {
        document.getElementById('radio_location_any').checked = true;
       } else {
        document.getElementById('radio_location_specific').checked = true;
       }
       if ('' == 'Specific Date') {
        document.getElementById('radio_date_date').checked = true;
       } else {
        document.getElementById('radio_date_imm').checked = true;
       }
                        }
                    };

                    domready(function() {
                        AppxPostJob.init();
                    });

                //]]>
    </script>

                //<![CDATA[
                var redirectUserToExtContent = {
                    listingUrl : '',
                    listingId : '',
                    listingType : '',
                    listingInternalArticle : true,
                    listingExternalContent : false,


                    setValues : function(e){
                        redirectUserToExtContent.listingUrl = e.getAttribute('data-listing-url');
                        redirectUserToExtContent.listingId = e.getAttribute('data-listing-id');
                        redirectUserToExtContent.listingType = e.getAttribute('data-listing-type');
                        redirectUserToExtContent.listingInternalArticle = e.getAttribute('data-listing-internalArticle');
                        redirectUserToExtContent.listingExternalContent = redirectUserToExtContent.listingType === 'Content' && redirectUserToExtContent.listingInternalArticle === 'false';
                    },
                    redirect : function(){
                        Visualforce.remoting.Manager.invokeAction('AppxLayoutController.createExternalContentUA', redirectUserToExtContent.listingId, redirectUserToExtContent.listingType, redirectUserToExtContent.listingInternalArticle, Appx.getCookie("apex__appxSearch"),function(result, event){
                                    if(event.status){
                                        if(true){
                                            expires = "; expires=0";
                                            document.cookie = 'apex__appxSearch=' + encodeURI(result)+ expires + "; path=/";
                                        }
                                        window.location = redirectUserToExtContent.listingUrl;
                                    }

                                },
                                {escape:true}
                        );
                    },
                    evaluateRedirection : function(){
                        if(redirectUserToExtContent.listingExternalContent){
                            redirectUserToExtContent.redirect();
                        }else{
                            window.location = redirectUserToExtContent.listingUrl;
                        }
                    }
                }
                if(sendClickEvent === undefined){
                    var sendClickEvent = function (element){

                        var analyticData = element.getAttribute('data-analytic');
                        if(analyticData.trim().length > 0){ // if contains analyticData is a search result or recomendation tile
                            Eventbus.publish('coveo_search_click', element);
                        }else{
                            Eventbus.publish('coveo_custom_click', element);
                        }
                    }
                };

                CoveoEventManager.hoverRemoteAction = 'AppxEventTile.analyticsHover';
                CoveoEventManager.tileViewRemoteAction = 'AppxEventTile.analyticsTileView';
                CoveoEventManager.screenShotRemoteAction = 'AppxEventTile.analyticsScreenShot';
                CoveoEventManager.clickRemoteAction = 'AppxEventTile.analyticClick';
                CoveoEventManager.customClickRemoteAction = 'AppxEventTile.customClick';
                CoveoEventManager.tabSwitchRemoteAction = 'AppxEventTile.analyticsListingTabSwitch';
                AppxTile.disallowedTypes = '[Job, Developer]';
                CoveoEventManager.initialize(userAnalyticsToken);
                //]]>
            </script>

<script class="optanon-category-3" type="text/plain">
        // <![CDATA[
        (function(cookieName, collectionEnabled){

                var oldCookie = Appx.getCookie(collection_config.oldCookieName);
                var newCookie = Appx.getCookie(cookieName);

                if (newCookie && oldCookie) {
                    var date = new Date();
                    date.setTime(date.getDate() - 1);
                    var expires = "; expires=" + date.toUTCString();
                    document.cookie = collection_config.oldCookieName + '=' + "" + expires +';path=/;secure';
                }

        })(collection_config.cookieName, collection_config.enabled);
        (function(token, cookieName){
            var isCookiePresent = Appx.getCookie(cookieName);
            if (!isCookiePresent || token !== isCookiePresent) {
                const d = new Date();
                d.setTime(d.getTime() + (30 * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000));
                let expires = d.toUTCString();
                document.cookie = cookieName + '=' + token + ';expires=' + expires +';path=/;secure';
            }
        })(userAnalyticsToken, collection_config.cookieName)

        //]]>
    </script>
<script type="text/javascript">
        //<![CDATA[
        var spinnerData;
        function loadMoreListingsJS() {
            AppxFavorites.showSpinnerButton();
            Appx.disableButton('appx-load-more-button-id');
            loadMore();
            return false;
        }

        function loadMoreListingsLevel2() {
            Appx.showSpinnerButton('appx-load-more-button-specialists');
            Appx.disableButton('appx-load-more-button-specialists');
            loadMoreLevel2();
            return false;
        }

        function loadMoreListingsLevel1() {
            Appx.showSpinnerButton('appx-load-more-button-certNav');
            Appx.disableButton('appx-load-more-button-certNav');
            loadMoreLevel1();
            return false;
        }

        // function loadMoreListingsCertProf() {
        //     Appx.showSpinnerButton('appx-load-more-button-certProf');
        //     Appx.disableButton('appx-load-more-button-certProf');
        //     loadMoreCertifiedProf();
        //     return false;
        // }

        function onCompleteFunctionSpecialists() {
            var tableAjax = document.getElementById('ajax-result');

            var elems = tableAjax.children;
            var tbody = document.getElementById('appx-table-results-specialists');
            for(var i = 0; i < tableAjax.children.length; i++) {
                tbody.appendChild(tableAjax.children[i].cloneNode(true));
            }
            tableAjax.innerHTML = '';

            AppxTile.init();
            disableLoadMoreSpecialists();
            Appx.hideSpinnerButton('appx-load-more-button-specialists');
            Appx.enableButton('appx-load-more-button-specialists');
        }

        function onCompleteFunctionCertNav() {
            var tableAjax = document.getElementById('ajax-result');

            var elems = tableAjax.children;
            var tbody = document.getElementById('appx-table-results-certNav');
            for(var i = 0; i < tableAjax.children.length; i++) {
                tbody.appendChild(tableAjax.children[i].cloneNode(true));
            }
            tableAjax.innerHTML = '';

            AppxTile.init();
            disableLoadMoreCertNav();
            Appx.hideSpinnerButton('appx-load-more-button-certNav');
            Appx.enableButton('appx-load-more-button-certNav');
        }

        function onCompleteFunction() {
            var tiles = [];
            var move_to = function(element, append_to) {
                tiles.push(element.getElementsByClassName('appx-tile')[0]);
                append_to.appendChild(element.cloneNode(true));
            };

            if (true){
                var tableAjax = document.getElementById('ajax-result');
                var tbody = document.getElementById('appx-table-results');
                for(var i = 0; i < tableAjax.children.length; i++) {
                    move_to(tableAjax.children[i], tbody);
                }
                tableAjax.innerHTML = '';
            }
            else{
                var table = document.getElementById('new-rows-table');
                var tbody = document.getElementById('appx-results-table-body');

                table.querySelectorAll('tr').forEach(function(element){
                    tbody.appendChild(element.cloneNode(true));
                    element.remove();
                });
            }
            AppxTile.init();
            disableLoadMore();
            AppxFavorites.hideSpinnerButton();
            Appx.enableButton('appx-load-more-button-id');
            SendAnalyticsCustomEvents.asyncTilesEvent(tiles);
        }

        function applyingSortJS(){
            spinnerData = AppxSpinnerManager.wholePageOrContent('content');
        }

        function sortAppliedJS(){
